Stuff I learned while coding this module

loopback
--.json files used for creating custom endpoints (i.e. service calls)

loopback-component-storage
--root json config specified folder must exist for server to start up properly
--need a level of indirection between db and file system (e.g. PostImage & ImageFile)

sharp
--can be imported into a .js file : require('sharp')
--allows image manipulation

fs
--filesystem manipulation : require('fs')

